Program: Omnibus
Title: Cementing the Ties
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376m5k
Last Broadcast Date: 12 April 2001
The story of a group of teachers from Oldham who went on a fact-finding mission to Bangladesh to gain a better understanding of their pupils' culture outside school. They talk of the lasting and profound effect it has had on their lives.